To install the knowledge base 'duck' sample, execute the following
commands from the <installdir>/samples/kb sub-directory:

% cp classes/duck.clp ../../kb/classes
% cp rules/duck.clp ../../kb/rules
% echo "(load* classes/duck.clp)" >> ../../kb/classes/load.clp
% echo "(load* rules/duck.clp)" >> ../../kb/rules/load.clp

Using an editor, manually merge the <msg>...</msg> entries in
data/msg_en.xmc into ../../kb/data/msg_en.xmc.
